MakeTestsBetter
===============

Tired of writing bad code?
Finding it tough to maintain your test suite?
Maybe, just maybe, TestsBetter can help you get through it.

Using cutting edge debugging tricks,
and AI patterns developed by the military,
MakeTestsBetter will transform your Test::Unit suite with only a few keypresses.

"rake away the pain!"

Example
=======

got a failing test???

>> ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/matthewrudy/make_tests_better

and a quick

 >> rake test BETTER=true
or
 >> rake test:better

and your troubles will be no more.

